<p>所以可得样本方差<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span></span></span></span>做分母和真实方差的关系为：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable rowspacing="0.25em" columnalign="right left" columnspacing="0em"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant="double-struck">E</mi><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><mover accent="true"><mi>x</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant="double-struck">E</mi><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><msup><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><mi>μ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mover accent="true"><mi>x</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mi>μ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant="double-struck">E</mi><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><mi>μ</mi><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="double-struck">E</mi><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mover accent="true"><mi>x</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><mo>−</mo><mi>μ</mi><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant="double-struck">E</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mi>σ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><msup><mi>σ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><msup><mi>σ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><msup><mi>σ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><msup><mi>σ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\begin{aligned}
&amp;\mathbb{E}\left(\frac{\sum_{i=1}^n(x_i-\bar{x})^2}{n}\right)\\
=&amp;\mathbb{E}\left(\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n\left[(x_i-\mu)-(\bar{x}-\mu)\right]^2\right)\\
=&amp;\mathbb{E}\left(\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(x_i-\mu)^2\right)-\mathbb{E}\left((\bar{x}-\mu)^2\right)\\
=&amp;\mathbb{E}(\sigma^2)-\frac{1}{n}\sigma^2\\
=&amp;\sigma^2-\frac{1}{n}\sigma^2\\
=&amp;\frac{n-1}{n}\sigma^2
